dialogStrings:
“You say you don't know when the stars
are gonna fall from the sky?
Is that for real?”{PAUSE}“I still don't believe it!
How could this happen?”

“Ancient Weapon? End of the world?
Malarky!
I'm gonna live to be a hundred!”{PAUSE}“There's still tons of stuff I gotta do!
This's just the beginning.”

“And what have Shinra and SOLDIER
done about it? Tell me!
They're useless!!”

“Actually, I'm a beautiful maid.
I only work in this accessory
store part-time.”{PAUSE}“Our goods compare
with the best goods anywhere.
So, how about one?”
